      </p>

      <div class="space-x-4">
        <a
          href="/ecole"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-red-900 font-bold rounded-full text-2xl hover:bg-red-200 transition-colors shadow-lg"
        >
          Réessayer
        </a>
        <a
          href="/"
          class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white font-bold rounded-full text-2xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
